{"word":"ἔτος","slug":"ἔτος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἔτος, ους, τό</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Lat.\">Lat.</a> vetus ‘old’] <b>year <a href='B:470 9:20'>Mt 9:20</a>; <a href='B:490 2:36'>Lk 2:36</a>; <a href='B:500 2:20'>J 2:20</a>; <a href='B:510 4:22'>Ac 4:22</a>; <a href='B:510 19:10'>19:10</a>; <a href='B:550 1:18'>Gal 1:18</a>; <a href='B:610 5:9'>1 Ti 5:9</a>; <a href='B:650 1:12'>Hb 1:12</a>; <a href='B:680 3:8'>2 Pt 3:8</a>; <a href='B:730 20:2-7'>Rv 20:2-7</a>.</b> <el>–ϰατ</el>’ <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔτος\">ἔτος</a></el> every year, annually <b><a href='B:490 2:41'>Lk 2:41</a>.</b> <el>ἔτη ἔχειν</el> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> numeral: of period of illness <b><a href='B:500 5:5'>J 5:5</a>;</b> of age <b><a href='B:500 8:57'>8:57</a>.</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀπὸ\">ἀπὸ</a> πολλῶν ἔτων</el> for many years <b><a href='B:520 15:23'>Ro 15:23</a>.</b> <el>πρὸ ἐτῶν δεϰατεσσάρων</el> fourteen years ago <b><a href='B:540 12:2'>2 Cor 12:2</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἑτοίμως\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐτύθην\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}